1019
01:15:18,139 --> 01:15:20,222
I love you.

1020
01:15:23,477 --> 01:15:25,389
Yes, I'll leave.

1021
01:15:32,319 --> 01:15:34,561
Have mercy on me.

1022
01:15:35,865 --> 01:15:37,527
I beg you.

1023
01:15:38,242 --> 01:15:41,076
Allow me for one moment to believe

1024
01:15:41,162 --> 01:15:44,576
