1025
01:15:46,500 --> 01:15:48,116
Lie to me.

1026
01:15:49,420 --> 01:15:50,661
I'll believe you.

1027
01:15:52,423 --> 01:15:54,506
I'll ardently believe you.

1028
01:15:58,512 --> 01:16:00,174
I beg you.

1029
01:16:04,060 --> 01:16:06,097
