by my handling of this matter.

1076
01:19:32,559 --> 01:19:38,726
It's sad, not to mention unartistic,
to have to admit love's victory

1077
01:19:38,816 --> 01:19:41,775
and evil's utter defeat.

1078
01:19:45,072 --> 01:19:47,735
