1079
01:19:49,076 --> 01:19:50,317
Leave me.

1080
01:19:58,085 --> 01:20:03,626
Don Juan might grace me
with his company for a short while.

1081
01:20:07,594 --> 01:20:10,837
I can't say that I love you, Master.

1082
01:20:10,931 --> 01:20:14,345
